data.description: Welcome to this spacious, move-in ready home! This townhouse is one of the larger models in the community, at a total of 2,116 square feet. It features a separate living room and dining room with gleaming wood-like floors throughout. The dining room could be a great space for hosting holiday dinners and entertaining. In addition, there are stainless steel appliances, main-level laundry, a primary bedroom with an ensuite bathroom & walk-in closet, fenced in backyard, and a spacious basement. The basement is an open canvas for a dream she/man cave, rec room, office, bonus room, or whatever your heart desires. It also includes a separate storage room, workshop space, and egress door. The home comes with two assigned parking spaces. The community includes a playground and community center. The neighborhood is conveniently located near Royal Farms and Sunoco gas stations, shopping centers, and route 40. Wow, all of this under $240,000!
